title: Propulsion Assignment
description: The assignment is available online. Submit a link to the landing page of your Web application running on Netlify. The landing page should include the following: Your full name and section Links to each of the lab assignments Link to the Kanbas application Links to all relevant source code repositories The Kanbas application should include a link to navigate back to the landing page.

title: Combustion Analysis
description: Analyze combustion processes in rocket engines and provide detailed calculations of efficiency and performance metrics.

title: Nozzle Design Project
description: Design and optimize a rocket nozzle for maximum thrust efficiency. Include CAD drawings and performance calculations.

title: Aerodynamics Quiz
description: Complete the online quiz covering fundamental aerodynamics principles including lift, drag, and boundary layer theory.

title: Flow Analysis
description: Perform computational fluid dynamics analysis on provided airfoil geometries and submit detailed report.

title: Heating Analysis
description: Analyze thermal heating effects during atmospheric reentry and propose thermal protection strategies.

title: Structural Design Task
description: Design the structural framework for a spacecraft component considering stress, fatigue, and safety factors.

title: Orbital Calculations
description: Calculate orbital parameters for satellite deployment including velocity, altitude, and transfer orbits.

title: Systems Engineering Exam
description: Comprehensive exam covering all aspects of spacecraft systems engineering including propulsion, power, and communications.

title: Organic Chemistry Problem Set 1
description: Complete the assigned problems on functional groups and stereochemistry. Upload a single PDF of your work.

title: Organic Chemistry Lab Report
description: Write a short lab report summarizing procedure, results, and discussion for the most recent synthesis lab.

title: Inorganic Chemistry Worksheet
description: Answer the worksheet questions on coordination compounds and bonding. Submit as PDF.

title: Inorganic Chemistry Mini-Quiz
description: Complete the online quiz covering crystal field theory basics.

title: Physical Chemistry Homework 1
description: Solve the assigned thermodynamics problems and show all work. Submit a PDF.

title: Kinetics Quiz
description: Short online quiz on reaction rate laws and integrated rate equations.

title: Quenya/Sindarin Translation Exercise
description: Translate the provided phrases and identify key grammar features. Submit answers as a document or PDF.
